@baseUrl = http://localhost:8005/api

### 1. Health Check
GET {{baseUrl}}/system/health

### 2. Database Statistics & TMDB Enrichment Progress
GET {{baseUrl}}/system/stats

### 3. User Registration
# @name register
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "developer",
  "email": "dev@example.com",
  "password": "strongpassword123"
}

### 4. User Login (Obtain Access Token)
# @name login
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/login
Content-Type: application/x-www-form-urlencoded

username=developer&password=strongpassword123

### 5. Get Current Authenticated Profile
GET {{baseUrl}}/auth/me
Authorization: Bearer {{login.response.body.access_token}}

### ========== BROWSE & SEARCH (PAGINATED) ==========

### 6. Browse All Movies (Page 1, sorted by popularity)
GET {{baseUrl}}/movies/browse?page=1&page_size=10&sort_by=popularity&order=desc

### 7. Browse Page 2
GET {{baseUrl}}/movies/browse?page=2&page_size=10&sort_by=popularity&order=desc

### 8. Browse Movies sorted by TMDB rating
GET {{baseUrl}}/movies/browse?page=1&page_size=10&sort_by=vote_average&order=desc

### 9. Browse Movies sorted alphabetically
GET {{baseUrl}}/movies/browse?page=1&page_size=20&sort_by=title&order=asc

### 10. Search Movies (Paginated)
GET {{baseUrl}}/movies/search?q=Toy Story&page=1&page_size=10

### 11. Search with more results
GET {{baseUrl}}/movies/search?q=Batman&page=1&page_size=5

### 12. Search Page 2
GET {{baseUrl}}/movies/search?q=Batman&page=2&page_size=5

### ========== SINGLE MOVIE ==========

### 13. Get Single Movie Details
GET {{baseUrl}}/movies/1

### ========== RATINGS ==========

### 14. Submit Movie Rating
POST {{baseUrl}}/ratings/
Authorization: Bearer {{login.response.body.access_token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "movie_id": 1,
  "rating": 5.0
}

### 15. Rate another movie
POST {{baseUrl}}/ratings/
Authorization: Bearer {{login.response.body.access_token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "movie_id": 356,
  "rating": 4.5
}

### 16. Rate another movie
POST {{baseUrl}}/ratings/
Authorization: Bearer {{login.response.body.access_token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "movie_id": 318,
  "rating": 5.0
}

### 17. Get Rating History (Paginated)
GET {{baseUrl}}/ratings/history?page=1&page_size=10
Authorization: Bearer {{login.response.body.access_token}}

### ========== RECOMMENDATIONS ==========

### 18. Get Personalized Hybrid Recommendations (with TMDB poster URLs, cast, overview)
GET {{baseUrl}}/recommendations/
Authorization: Bearer {{login.response.body.access_token}}

### ========== SIMILAR MOVIES ==========

### 19. Get Similar Movies (Content-Based — uses 8-channel TF-IDF)
GET {{baseUrl}}/movies/1/similar?method=content&limit=5

### 20. Get Similar Movies (Collaborative — uses SVD latent space)
GET {{baseUrl}}/movies/1/similar?method=collaborative&limit=5

### ========== SYSTEM ADMIN ==========

### 21. Get System Metrics (RMSE, NDCG, Coverage, etc.)
GET {{baseUrl}}/system/metrics

### 22. Trigger TMDB Enrichment (requires TMDB_API_KEY in .env)
POST {{baseUrl}}/system/enrich

### 23. Trigger Model Retraining
POST {{baseUrl}}/system/train
